# .understandignore - patterns for files/dirs to exclude from analysis
# Syntax: same as .gitignore (globs, comments, ! negation, trailing / for dirs).
# Scope: project root. Keep Kalman/, MPC/, docs, tests, and migrations included.

# Environment and local secrets.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example

# Python runtime output.
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.venv/
venv/
env/
*.egg-info/
pip-wheel-metadata/

# Node/frontend generated output.
node_modules/
dist/
build/
out/
.vite/
coverage/
playwright-report/
test-results/
*.tsbuildinfo
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Local editors and OS metadata.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Runtime, temporary, and generated Understand outputs.
*.log
tmp/
temp/
.cache/
.understand-anything/intermediate/
.understand-anything/tmp/
.understand-anything/knowledge-graph.json
.understand-anything/meta.json
.understand-anything/fingerprints.json
.understand-anything/review.json

# Large or derived project artifacts that do not improve code graph quality.
ARX/*.csv
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.joblib
MPC/reports/

# External agent skill mirrors copied into the repo.
.claude/.claude/skills/.antigravitySkill/
.claude/.claude/skills/.claudeSkill/
.claude/.claude/skills/.codexSkill/
.claude/.claude/skills/.cursorSkill/
.claude/.claude/skills/.opencodeSkill/
